The paper discusses text steganography methods and their detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of statistical analysis in steganalysis suggests a focus on machine learning and data analysis (cs.LG), as well as natural language processing (cs.CL). Information theory (cs.IT) is also relevant to the study of steganography. Finally, multimedia (cs.MM) may be relevant if the paper discusses the use of steganography in images or videos.
